room_title: Escape room "Monica’s Apartment" by Legends of Xscape in West Palm Beach
room_address: 324 Datura St, Suite 101, West Palm Beach, FL 33401
room_description: Grab your friends and head over to 495 Grove Street for a night of fun and games with the gang…until Phoebe looses her purse. Ross changed the door code and only Phoebe knows  the code. You have 60 mins before Monica has a full on breakdown and Joey is late for his audition.
